                <h1>You hate Duke, and you might be the reason why</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/de80fad1-917b-4c66-a94e-c5d29885f129.sized-1000x1000.png?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
